<ol type="A">
<li>The majority of all members of the Board shall be necessary to constitute a quorum for the transaction of business.</li>
<li>RHAM Board of Education has 11 members. Six members of the Board of Education shall constitute a quorum.</li>
<li>Quorum will be determined by the number of present members and the number of members calling to the meeting.</li>
</ol>
